title: Ask HN: What's a Web 3.0 consumer idea that can take off?
text:
Most of the big Crypto / Web 3.0 ideas are restricted to infra, defi, gaming or NFT projects. I have yet to see a Web 3.0 consumer idea that has taken off.

Any predictions here ?
